HEADWORD: Spermophyta
<hw>Sper*moph"y*ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[Nl.,
from Gr. <grk>spe`rma</grk> a seed + <grk>fyto`n</grk> a plant.]</ety>
<def>Plants which produce seed; phaenogamia. These plants constitute the
highest grand division of the vegetable kingdom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

